title.rendered: Box of 50, Sentry Mediam 210 Low Adherent Dressing 10x10cm

content.rendered:
Mediam 210 Low Adherent Dressing consists of a heavy gauge and highly absorbent inner pad encased between two layers of highly embossed polyethylene film.

Suitable For:

  • Light to moderate exuding wounds
  • Cuts and grazes
  • Minor burns

Product Features:

  • Film minimises adherence of dressing to the wound
  • Highly absorbent
  • Double sided
